quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  2,47,"Mwebwe ruvyaro rwa bene israeri, nimwibuke imigisha yanje nabahaye hamwe n’iteka nabateye gusumba ibindi biremwa vyose"
  2,48,"Kandi mutinye wamusi umutima w’umuntu ataco uzofasha uwundi mutima kukintu icarico cose, kandi ntihazo kwemerwa ibisabisho vyanyu, kandi ntihazo kwakirwa icoba kombora kivuye kuriwe, kandi ntibazoronka ikizoba kingira"
  2,49,"No mugihe twarokora abantu bokwa Fir’auni aribo babahaye ibihano bibi cane mugukerera ibibondo vyanyu vy’abahungu, n’ugusigaza ibibondo vy’abigeme\tgusa,\tnomuri\tivyo\tharabonetse\timigisha\tmininiya\tivuye k’Umuremyi wanyu"
  2,50,"Mugihe twatandukanya ikiyaga kubera mwebwe n’ukubarokora, duca twibiza abantu bokwa Fir’auni namwe mwibonera"
  2,51,"N’igihe twemerera intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) amajoro mirongo ine, hanyuma muca mugira intama munyuma yiwe nukuba mubahemukiye imitima yanyu"
  2,52,"Mu nyuma yaho twaciye tubagirira ikigongwe, kugira ngo mube mu bantu bakenguruka"
  2,53,Mugihe twamuha intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) igitabu c’ugutandukanya hagati y’ibirimwo vy’ukuri hamwe n’ibitari ivy’ukuri kugira ngo murokoke
  2,54,"N’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) mugihe yabwira abantu biwe avuga ati:- bantu banje! mu vy’ukuri mwebwe mwara hemukiye imitima yanyu mukugira intama kuba ariyo Mana yanyu, rero nimusabe\tikigongwe\tcinshi\tku\tMuremyi\twanyu,\tkandi\tmwice\tiyo\tmitima yanyu, ivyo nivyo vyiza imbere y’Umuremyi wanyu, nayo ica yakira imbabazi zanyu, mu vy’ukuri niyo yakira izo mbabazi, kandi niyo nyene impuhwe zihagije"
  2,55,"N’igihe mwavuga muti:- ewe ntumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) twebwe ntituzo kwemera kugeza aho tuzobona Imana imbona nkubone, muca musokorwa n’urupfu giturumbuka namwe muraba"
  2,56,Hanyuma turabazura munyuma y’ukwitaba Umuremyi wanyu kugira ngo muyikengurukire
  2,57,"Tubashiriraho igitutu c’ibicu n’ukuba manurira ibipfungurwa vyitiriwe Manna hamwe na Salwa, rero nimufungure kuri ibi bifungurwa vyiza twabahaye, nabo rero ntiba hemukira twebwe, mugabo nibo bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  2,58,"N’igihe twavuga duti:- nimwinjire muri iki gisagara hanyuma mufungure mwidegemvya aho mushaka hose, kandi mwinjire murugi rwayo n’ubugamburutsi ntangere, kandi muvuge muti:- tugirire ikigongwe kubera ibicumuro vyacu, natwe tuzoba girira ikigongwe c’amakosa yanyu, kandi tuzobongereza ineza kuri bamwe bagira ineza"
  2,59,"Abahemukiye imitima yabo nuko bahinduye imvugo atari iyo babwiwe, duca tumanura hejuru yabamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo ibihano bininiya bivuye mw’ijuru kubera ukwiyonkora kwabo"